<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:13:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾商业团体在南海紧张局势中罕见发表声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-business-groups-make-rare-statement-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-06-21/</link><description>菲律宾商业团体周五表示，他们对菲律宾军方的骚扰表示遗憾，这是在海军人员与中国海警最近在有争议的南海发生冲突之后发表的评论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-business-groups-make-rare-statement-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国贸易重心可能从中国转向美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-trade-focus-could-pivot-china-us-2024-06-21/</link><description>经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克将在周五开始的访问中强调德国寻求与中国建立商业联系的决心，但贸易专家表示，经济和政治因素都越来越有利于美德关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-trade-focus-could-pivot-china-us-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国称欧盟贸易摩擦升级可能引发“贸易战”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-says-eu-escalation-trade-friction-could-trigger-trade-war-2024-06-21/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟贸易摩擦持续升级，“可能引发贸易战”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:11:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-says-eu-escalation-trade-friction-could-trigger-trade-war-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商继续掌控东南亚蓬勃发展的电动汽车市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-retain-grip-over-southeast-asias-booming-electric-car-market-2024-06-21/</link><description>Counterpoint Research 周五表示，在中国比亚迪和越南 VinFast 的带动下，东南亚电动汽车销量激增，蚕食了日本和韩国公司主导的内燃机汽车市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-retain-grip-over-southeast-asias-booming-electric-car-market-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>华为表示，从操作系统到人工智能，它已经取得了巨大进步</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-says-it-has-made-huge-strides-operating-systems-ai-2024-06-21/</link><description>中国华为技术有限公司(HWT.UL)周五表示，该公司在从操作系统到人工智能等领域都取得了突破，该公司用了10年的时间才完成了美国和欧洲花了30年才实现的目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-says-it-has-made-huge-strides-operating-systems-ai-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>飞机租赁商DAE认为中国商飞将打破空客、波音双寡头垄断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aircraft-lessor-dae-sees-chinas-comac-breaking-airbus-boeing-duopoly-2024-06-21/</link><description>飞机租赁公司迪拜航空航天企业公司（DAE）负责人告诉路透社，中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司有机会在未来十年打破空客和波音在客机市场的双寡头垄断。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:31:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aircraft-lessor-dae-sees-chinas-comac-breaking-airbus-boeing-duopoly-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>现金再次离开中国，人民币承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/cash-is-leaving-china-again-pressuring-yuan-2024-06-21/</link><description>人民币贬值和大量现金从内地流入香港表明，中国国内投资者正在搁置对国内市场立即复苏的预期，并纷纷转向最接近的收益率更高的资产。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/cash-is-leaving-china-again-pressuring-yuan-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国威胁对“顽固”台独分子判处死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-guidelines-criminal-punishment-diehard-taiwan-separatists-2024-06-21/</link><description>中国周五威胁要对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑，尽管中国法院对这个民主治理的岛屿没有管辖权，但压力却不断加大。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-guidelines-criminal-punishment-diehard-taiwan-separatists-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国要求维萨卡和万事达卡降低交易费用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-visa-mastercard-cut-transaction-fees-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-06-21/</link><description>据彭博社援引一位知情人士的话报道，中国正在推动维萨卡和万事达卡降低其在中国的银行卡交易费用，作为便利外国游客支付的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-visa-mastercard-cut-transaction-fees-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港人拥抱英国政治，但有些人仍然害怕北京</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kongers-embrace-politics-uk-some-still-fear-beijing-2024-06-21/</link><description>对于两年前从香港移居英国的 25 岁理查德·黄 (Richard Wong) 来说，参加自由选举、行使他曾经争取过的权利“感觉很奇怪”，但他知道他家乡的朋友已经不能再这样做了。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kongers-embrace-politics-uk-some-still-fear-beijing-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通财富主管认为中国经济前景改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/jpmorgan-wealth-head-sees-chinas-economic-outlook-improving-2024-06-21/</link><description>摩根大通资产和财富管理首席执行官玛丽·埃尔多斯表示，摩根大通看到中国经济好转的迹象，这将提振该行在经历了低迷时期后在中国的业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/jpmorgan-wealth-head-sees-chinas-economic-outlook-improving-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>越南表示愿意与菲律宾讨论马尼拉的联合国海事主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vietnam-says-willing-talk-philippines-about-manilas-un-maritime-claim-2024-06-21/</link><description>在马尼拉上周向联合国提出南海扩展大陆架主张后，越南周五表示，愿意与菲律宾对话，寻求符合两国利益的措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vietnam-says-willing-talk-philippines-about-manilas-un-maritime-claim-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国预计中国之行不会解决欧盟关税紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-doesnt-expect-solution-eu-tariff-tensions-china-trip-2024-06-21/</link><description>在欧盟威胁对中国汽车征收高额关税后，德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克预计不会在中国之行中就贸易紧张局势达成解决方案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-doesnt-expect-solution-eu-tariff-tensions-china-trip-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚寻求国防部长与中国对话以减少军事事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-seeks-defence-chiefs-dialogue-with-china-reduce-military-incidents-2024-06-21/</link><description>澳大利亚国防部长理查德·马勒斯周五表示，澳大利亚希望与中国国防部长重启年度对话，以减少两军之间的误解，并于本周向中国总理李强提出了此事。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:24:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-seeks-defence-chiefs-dialogue-with-china-reduce-military-incidents-2024-06-21/</guid></item><item><title>日本对支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争的中国企业实施贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-imposes-trade-curbs-china-based-firms-supporting-russias-war-ukraine-2024-06-21/</link><description>日本外交部周五在一份声明中表示，日本对中国企业实施贸易限制，这是对支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争的个人和团体实施新一轮制裁的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-imposes-trade-curbs-china-based-firms-supporting-russias-war-ukraine-2024-06-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>